BT 1 0 0 1 0 61 Tm /F1 9 Tf 14 TL (A 4096-token response at 380 t/s still takes 11 seconds to complete. For a game, that is an unacceptable freeze.) Tj T* (Streaming shows the first token in under half a second and gives the player the feeling of a thinking, breathing entity.) Tj T* (NPCs that type their responses feel alive. Loading screens that narrate what is happening feel dynamic. Streaming is) Tj T* (the single biggest UX improvement for in-game AI. The bridge sends Server-Sent Events \(SSE\). GDScript reads them) Tj T* (via HTTPClient in chunked mode \227 HTTPRequest cannot do this, it buffers the entire response.) Tj T* ET
