e. Savings: ~90% on SCENE_CONTEXT tokens after first call. """ full_prompt =) Tj T* (SCENE_CONTEXT + "\\n\\n" + question result = await gemini_complete\(full_prompt, thinking=thinking\) # Log) Tj T* (cache savings cached = result.get\("cached", 0\) total = result.get\("tokens", 0\) saved_usd = cached * 0.9 *) Tj T* (\(0.50 / 1_000_000\) if cached > 0: print\(f"[cache] {cached}/{total} tokens cached \267 ~${saved_usd:.5f}) Tj T* (saved this call"\) return result) Tj T* ET
