BT 1 0 0 1 0 153.5 Tm /F5 7.5 Tf 11.5 TL (extends Node ## When the player does something significant, the world notices. ## NPCs gossip about it.) Tj T* (Books mention it. Signs warn about it. var significant_events: Array[Dictionary] = [] func) Tj T* (player_did\(action: String, location: String, details: Dictionary\) -> void: var event := { "action":) Tj T* (action, "location": location, "details": details, "time": Time.get_ticks_msec\(\), }) Tj T* (significant_events.append\(event\) _propagate_event\(event\) func _propagate_event\(event: Dictionary\) ->) Tj T* (void: var prompt := \( "A player in a dark fantasy RPG just did this: " + JSON.stringify\(event\) + "\\n" +) Tj T* ("Generate 3 things: \(1\) a 1-sentence rumour an NPC might say, " + "\(2\) a 1-sentence journal entry a) Tj T* (witness would write, " + "\(3\) a short warning sign that might appear near the location. " + "Return JSON:) Tj T* ({rumour: string, journal: string, sign: string}" \) AIAgent.response_received.connect\( func\(text, _p\):) Tj T* (_apply_world_reaction\(text, event\), CONNECT_ONE_SHOT\) AIAgent.ask\(prompt, "minimal"\) func) Tj T* (_apply_world_reaction\(text: String, _event: Dictionary\) -> void: var s := text.find\("{"\); var e :=) Tj T* (text.rfind\("}"\)+1 if s == -1: return var data: Dictionary = JSON.parse_string\(text.substr\(s, e-s\)\)) Tj T* (WorldState.add_rumour\(data.get\("rumour", ""\)\) WorldState.add_journal_entry\(data.get\("journal", ""\)\) #) Tj T* (Spawn a procedural sign near the event location WorldState.spawn_sign\(data.get\("sign", ""\)\)) Tj T* ET
